{"tid":892381,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"體臭一問","createTime":"2018-11-07T00:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T13:25:13.000Z","uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"790f0a404d0d989adbb09bdd34ead6e8fb6d0a2e","tid":892381,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T00:07:36.000Z","msg":"我個Flatmate好撚臭 成日都有陣upup臭臭縮縮味 <br />\n<br />\n明明英國既天氣唔會點流汗 同埋佢一日已經沖兩次涼<br />\n<br />\n仲成日散發住陣臭味 行過都聞到 沖完涼個廁所仲臭過未沖之前 <br />\n<br />\n之前試過買止汗劑比佢 又試過係佢身上噴空氣清新劑<br />\n<br />\n而家點左佢用滴露開水浸浴 <br />\n<br />\n仲有咩方法交流下  <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1556a9f7dc53c7908db10361bfd60b5b629487d5","tid":892381,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T00:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652ef4e91e29702ec562914104ef297abdaa48b4","tid":892381,"uid":145744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T00:39:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7389b98c3eb8db0c3d8ae348e252b3dcbdbe6066","tid":892381,"uid":179990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T01:04:46.000Z","msg":"改善下飲食習慣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b03422db1964745067e69486456246bedcd009a","tid":892381,"uid":128563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T01:06:11.000Z","msg":"會唔會係佢發霉呀，開抽濕機啦"},{"pid":"5735590e97ea88054720d5127ed46c71d56f66f0","tid":892381,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"652ef4e91e29702ec562914104ef297abdaa48b4","tid":892381,"uid":145744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T00:39:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T01:19:30.000Z","msg":"肥仔黎"},{"pid":"a987d0367ddf18c9a3c54bb2c5473c499dd7ca5c","tid":892381,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:56:53.000Z","msg":"買鯡魚罐頭蓋咗佢陣味"},{"p